# IPython in depth tutorial (EuroSciPy edition)

To get the tutorial, checkout the `euroscipy` branch of `ipython-in-depth`:

    $ git clone https://github.com/ipython/ipython-in-depth -b euroscipy

Or just download and unzip the branch:

    $ wget https://github.com/ipython/ipython-in-depth/zipball/euroscipy -O ipython-in-depth.zip
    # or
    $ curl -L https://github.com/ipython/ipython-in-depth/zipball/euroscipy -o ipython-in-depth.zip
    $ unzip ipython-in-depth.zip

To start the notebook server with the shipped `euroscipy` profile:

    $ cd /path/to/ipython-in-depth
    $ ipython notebook --ProfileDir.location=./profile_euroscipy

